sentences.sentence: "I tell people to look for unassigned problems," says Dr. Potter.
sentences.translation: “我告诉人们寻找未派职务的问题，”波特博士说。

sentences.sentence: One is to assign additional characters to presently unassigned 8-bit codes;
sentences.translation: 一种是把新字符赋以目前没使用到的8位码；

sentences.sentence: Unassigned citizens will notice dropped equipment outside the main area of your Kingdom.
sentences.translation: 未分配的市民会注意到下降设备你王国的主要区域之外。
